              training duration (1–40 hours). These improvements generalize
              across participants and out-of-sample movies, yielding robust
              cross-subject and cross-stimulus encoding. Second, a
              dual-objective loss that balances language modeling with brain
              alignment surpasses brain-only optimization, producing more stable
              and generalizable encoders. Finally, brain supervision enriches LM
